text: Charmbracelet is the ninth album by American singer-songwriter Mariah Carey. It was released on December 3, 2002. It was Carey's first album released by Island Records. ==Track listing== == References == Category:2002 albums Category:Mariah Carey albums Category:G-funk albums Category:Hip hop albums Category:R&B; albums Category:Island Records albums
